{"tid":2491202,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK ROSÉ 5月黑白畫報出爐：完美展示九頭身身材！","createTime":"2021-04-16T06:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T06:53:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f58f2faff83c0d6d7031bc352a310c05a85c5555","tid":2491202,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_b626820d161fb049fabe7c967d54ffb8/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-15/134878-903301.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_b626820d161fb049fabe7c967d54ffb8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-15%2F134878-903301.png&h=13485c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK成員ROS&Eacute;登上時尚雜誌《W Korea》五月刊，黑白畫風氣場十足！<br />\n<br />\n這組黑白大片中，有著「澳洲野玫瑰」之稱的ROS&Eacute;化身性感冷冽的黑玫瑰，又酷又飒，大秀好身材。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7d17f101b9d77e802db02ab6a8bb465d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-15/134878-903300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7d17f101b9d77e802db02ab6a8bb465d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-15%2F134878-903300.jpg&h=8c357fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_23613d21c2ccd7bfca12d21a5a8ef8aa/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-15/134878-903296.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_23613d21c2ccd7bfca12d21a5a8ef8aa%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-15%2F134878-903296.jpg&h=cda9de02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOversize西裝搭配超短褲，露出了驚艷的女團腿。 凌冽的眼神，隨風吹起的長髮為ROS&Eacute;增添冷漠感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e64578af6ff9e3dbdc48a846cccd0b51/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-15/134878-903297.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e64578af6ff9e3dbdc48a846cccd0b51%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-15%2F134878-903297.jpg&h=9f39e864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nROS&Eacute;引以為傲的腹肌螞蟻腰一定要展現出來，她側身看著鏡頭，滿臉的高冷表情，像極了要出外勤的女特工。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_17a5836ce0f8695600f71192c0dae48d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-15/134878-903298.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_17a5836ce0f8695600f71192c0dae48d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-15%2F134878-903298.jpg&h=9099c28d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臉部特寫是各大寫真不可少的環節，ROS&Eacute;的眼神如同黑洞一般讓人深陷，眼神把控到位，連手指都很有戲，這絕對是一張High Fashion照片了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_db510c4f7983597d25681758bd7b8c82/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-15/134878-903299.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_db510c4f7983597d25681758bd7b8c82%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-15%2F134878-903299.jpg&h=15e06071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，ROS&Eacute;最近發行的首張單曲《On The Ground》，成績非常不俗，是實力與顏值並存的優質愛豆。<br />\n<br />\n「圖：fb@W Korea 」"},{"pid":"41983e05f143fef6b305fb67a0d10d904ad287eb","tid":2491202,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"po多啲呢個彩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1e8179f49f2e6ce88619e4370d8295ff5501c0","tid":2491202,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fc0d727133f847b10ad5d500a30bf62e8e4fed","tid":2491202,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"正到癲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df0e2bde5a10613c3fbf6c5c1a02bf08e75fc78","tid":2491202,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"依個彩正 <br />\n但另一彩更正"},{"pid":"